51typedef struct { /* simple queue decl. */
52 int first;
53 int last;
54} _A_Q;
55
56/* create queue of symbols specified in parameter statements; keep
57 * separate queues for combinations of ansi-/vax- style parameters
58 * and those with A_CNST/non-A_CNST asts.
59 * 'first' locates first in the queue and is 0 if the queue is empty;
60 * symbols are linked together using the SYMLK field; queue is terminated
61 * when the SYMLK field is zero. 'last' locates the last parameter in
62 * the queue.
63 */
64static struct {
65 _A_Q q; /* queue for parameters with const ast's */
66 _A_Q q_e; /* queue for parameters with expr ast's */
67} params, vx_params = {0};

72} QSYM;

131static void
132push_indent(void)
133{
134 if (!ast_is_comment) {
135 indent++;
136 if (indent <= INDENT_MAX)
137 put_string(INDENT_STR);
138 }
139}

141static void
142pop_indent(void)
143{
144 if (!ast_is_comment) {
145 indent--;
146 if (indent < 0) {
147 interr("pop_indent:ident_level", indent, ERR_Warning);
148 indent = 0;
149 }
150 if (indent < INDENT_MAX)
151 col -= strlen(INDENT_STR);
152 }
153}

155static int
156precedence(int ast)
157{
158/*
159 * Precedence Levels:
160 * 20 identifiers, function calls, parens, etc.; any 'term'
161 * 18 **
162 * 16 * /
163 * 14 + - (binary)
164 * 12 + - (unary)
165 * 10 relationals
166 * 8 .not.
167 * 6 .and.
168 * 4 .or.
169 * 2 .neqv. .eqv.
170 */
171#define PREC_TERM 20
172#define PREC_POW 18
173#define PREC_MULT 16
174#define PREC_ADD 14
175#define PREC_NEG 12
176#define PREC_REL 10
177#define PREC_NOT 8
178#define PREC_AND 6
179#define PREC_OR 4
180#define PREC_EQV 2
181
182 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
183 case A_BINOP:
184 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
185 case OP_ADD:
186 case OP_SUB:
187 return PREC_ADD;
188 case OP_MUL:
189 case OP_DIV:
190 return PREC_MULT;
191 case OP_XTOI:
192 case OP_XTOX:
193 return PREC_POW;
194 case OP_CAT:
195 return PREC_MULT;
196 case OP_LEQV:
197 case OP_LNEQV:
198 return PREC_EQV;
199 case OP_LOR:
200 return PREC_OR;
201 case OP_LAND:
202 case OP_SCAND:
203 return PREC_AND;
204 case OP_EQ:
205 case OP_GE:
206 case OP_GT:
207 case OP_LE:
208 case OP_LT:
209 case OP_NE:
210 return PREC_REL;
211 default:
212 break;
213 }
214 break;
215 case A_UNOP:
216 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
217 case OP_ADD:
218 case OP_SUB:
219 return /* PREC_NEG */ PREC_ADD;
220 case OP_LNOT:
221 return PREC_NOT;
222 case OP_LOC:
223 case OP_REF:
224 case OP_VAL:
225 case OP_BYVAL:
226 break;
227 default:
228 break;
229 }
230 break;
231 case A_CONV:
232 return precedence((int)A_LOPG(ast));
233 default:
234 break;
235 }
236 return PREC_TERM;
237}

239static LOGICAL
240negative_constant(int ast)
241{
242 DBLINT64 inum1, inum2;
243 DBLE dnum1, dnum2;
244
245 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CNST) {
246 int sptr;
247 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
248 switch (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr))) {
249 case TY_INT:
250 if (CONVAL2G(sptr) & 0x80000000)
251 return TRUE;
252 break;
253 case TY_REAL:
254 if (xfcmp(CONVAL2G(sptr), CONVAL2G(stb.flt0)) < 0)
255 return TRUE;
256 break;
257 case TY_DBLE:
258 dnum1[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
259 dnum1[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
260 dnum2[0] = CONVAL1G(stb.dbl0);
261 dnum2[1] = CONVAL2G(stb.dbl0);
262 if (xdcmp(dnum1, dnum2) < 0)
263 return TRUE;
264 break;
265 case TY_INT8:
266 inum1[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
267 inum1[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
268 inum2[0] = 0;
269 inum2[1] = 0;
270 if (cmp64(inum1, inum2) < 0)
271 return TRUE;
272 break;
273 default:
274 break;
275 }
276 }
277 return FALSE;
278}

280static int
281left_precedence(int lop, int prec_op)
282{
283 int prec_lop;
284 while (A_TYPEG(lop) == A_CONV)
285 lop = A_LOPG(lop);
286 if (negative_constant(lop))
287 /*
288 * a constant represents the highest precedence level since it's
289 * a term. Treating it as a term is a problem if a negative constant
290 * is the left operand of a binary operator; the precedence needs to
291 * be the precedence of a unary minus.
292 */
293 return PREC_ADD;
294
295 prec_lop = precedence(lop);
296 if (prec_op == PREC_POW && prec_lop == PREC_POW)
297 /* left operand of ** is also a **; since '**' is right
298 * associative, need to ensure that the left operand is
299 * parenthesized.
300 */
301 prec_lop--;
302 return prec_lop;
303}
304
305static int
306right_precedence(int rop, int prec_op)
307{
308 int prec_rop;
309
310 while (A_TYPEG(rop) == A_CONV)
311 rop = A_LOPG(rop);
312 if (negative_constant(rop))
313 /*
314 * a constant represents the highest precedence level since it's
315 * a term. Treating it as a term is a problem if a negative constant
316 * is the right operand of a binary operator; the precedence needs to
317 * be the precedence of a unary minus.
318 */
319 return PREC_ADD;
320
321 prec_rop = precedence(rop);
322 if (prec_op == PREC_POW && prec_rop == PREC_POW)
323 /* right operand of ** is also a **; since '**' is right
324 * associative, need to ensure that the right operand is
325 * not parenthesized.
326 */
327 prec_rop++;
328 return prec_rop;
329}

359static void
360print_ast(int ast)
361{
362 const char *o;
363 int atype;
364 int i, asd;
365 int astli;
366 int argt;
367 int cnt;
368 int lop, rop;
369 int prec_op, prec_lop;
370 int shape;
371 LOGICAL encl;
372 int linearize;
373 LOGICAL save_op_space;
374 LOGICAL commutable, nid;
375 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn;
376 int sym, object;
377 int dtype;
378 int optype;
379 int save_dtype, save_comment;
380
381 switch (atype = A_TYPEG(ast)) {
382 case A_NULL:
383 break;
384 case A_ID:
385 print_refsym(A_SPTRG(ast), ast);
386 break;
387 case A_CNST:
388 put_const((int)A_SPTRG(ast));
389 break;
390 case A_LABEL:
391 if (altret_spec)
392 put_char('*');
393 put_string(label_name((int)A_SPTRG(ast)));
394 break;
395 case A_BINOP:
396 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
397 rop = A_ROPG(ast);
398 commutable = FALSE;
399 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
400 case OP_ADD:
401 o = "+";
402 commutable = TRUE;
403 break;
404 case OP_SUB:
405 o = "-";
406 break;
407 case OP_MUL:
408 o = "*";
409 commutable = TRUE;
410 break;
411 case OP_DIV:
412 o = "/";
413 break;
414 case OP_XTOI:
415 case OP_XTOX:
416 o = "**";
417 break;
418 case OP_CAT:
419 o = "//";
420 break;
421 case OP_LEQV:
422 o = ".eqv.";
423 commutable = TRUE;
424 break;
425 case OP_LNEQV:
426 o = ".neqv.";
427 commutable = TRUE;
428 break;
429 case OP_LOR:
430 o = ".or.";
431 commutable = TRUE;
432 break;
433 case OP_LAND:
434 case OP_SCAND:
435 o = ".and.";
436 commutable = TRUE;
437 break;
438 case OP_EQ:
439 o = ".eq.";
440 break;
441 case OP_GE:
442 o = ".ge.";
443 break;
444 case OP_GT:
445 o = ".gt.";
446 break;
447 case OP_LE:
448 o = ".le.";
449 break;
450 case OP_LT:
451 o = ".lt.";
452 break;
453 case OP_NE:
454 o = ".ne.";
455 break;
456 default:
457 o = "<bop>";
458 break;
459 }
460 if (commutable && (precedence(lop) > precedence(rop)) && !ast_is_comment) {
461 int tmp;
462 tmp = lop;
463 lop = rop;
464 rop = tmp;
465 }
466 prec_op = precedence(ast);
467 encl = prec_op > left_precedence(lop, prec_op);
468 if (encl)
469 put_char('(');
470 print_ast(lop);
471 if (encl)
472 put_char(')');
473 if (op_space)
474 put_char(' ');
475 put_l_to_u(o);
476 if (op_space)
477 put_char(' ');
478 encl = prec_op >= right_precedence(rop, prec_op);
479 if (encl)
480 put_char('(');
481 print_ast(rop);
482 if (encl)
483 put_char(')');
484 break;
485 case A_UNOP:
486 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
487 prec_lop = precedence(lop);
488 encl = precedence(ast) >= prec_lop;
489 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
490 case OP_ADD:
491 if (!encl && prec_lop != PREC_TERM)
492 o = "+ ";
493 else
494 o = "+";
495 break;
496 case OP_SUB:
497 if (negative_constant(lop))
498 encl = TRUE;
499 if (!encl && prec_lop != PREC_TERM)
500 o = "- ";
501 else
502 o = "-";
503 break;
504 case OP_LNOT:
505 o = ".not. ";
506 break;
507 case OP_LOC:
508 print_loc(lop);
509 return;
510 case OP_REF:
511 put_l_to_u("%ref(");
512 goto un_builtin;
513 case OP_BYVAL:
514 put_l_to_u("%byval(");
515 goto un_builtin;
516 case OP_VAL:
517 if (ast == astb.ptr0) {
518 put_string("pghpf_0(3)");
519 return;
520 }
521 if (ast == astb.ptr0c) {
522 put_string("pghpf_0c");
523 return;
524 }
525 put_l_to_u("%val(");
526 un_builtin:
527 print_ast(lop);
528 put_char(')');
529 return;
530 default:
531 o = "<uop>";
532 break;
533 }
534 put_l_to_u(o);
535 if (encl)
536 put_char('(');
537 print_ast(lop);
538 if (encl)
539 put_char(')');
540 break;
541 case A_CMPLXC:
542 put_char('(');
543 print_ast((int)A_LOPG(ast));
544 put_char(',');
545 print_ast((int)A_ROPG(ast));
546 put_char(')');
547 break;
548 case A_CONV:
549 print_ast((int)A_LOPG(ast));
550 break;
551 case A_PAREN:
552 put_char('(');
553 print_ast((int)A_LOPG(ast));
554 put_char(')');
555 break;
556 case A_MEM:
557 lop = (int)A_PARENTG(ast);
558 print_ast(lop);
559 dtype = A_DTYPEG(lop);
560 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_DERIVED)
561 put_char('%');
562 else
563 put_char('.');
564 print_ast(A_MEMG(ast));
565 break;
566 case A_SUBSCR:
567 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
568 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
569 linearize = pr_chk_arr(lop);
570 if (ast_is_comment)
571 linearize = 0;
572 if (XBIT(70, 8))
573 linearize = 0;
574 put_char('(');
575 save_op_space = op_space;
576 op_space = FALSE;
577 if (linearize == 1) {
578 /* if the output is standard f77, need to linearize the
579 * subscripts for subscripting an allocatable array.
580 */
581 int asym, dsym;
582 int dtype;
583 ADSC *ad;
584 int ln, lw, up, stride;
585
586 asym = memsym_of_ast(lop);
587 dsym = DESCRG(asym);
588 dtype = DTYPEG(dsym);
589 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY)
590 dtype = DTYPEG(asym);
591 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
592 dtype = DDTG(dtype); /* element type */
593 i = ASD_NDIM(asd) - 1;
594 lw = AD_LWAST(ad, i);
595 if (lw == 0)
596 lw = astb.i1;
597 ln = mk_binop(OP_SUB, (int)ASD_SUBS(asd, i), lw, astb.bnd.dtype);
598
599 for (i = i - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
600 lw = AD_LWAST(ad, i);
601 if (lw == 0)
602 lw = astb.bnd.one;
603 up = AD_UPAST(ad, i);
604 if (up == 0)
605 up = astb.bnd.one;
606 stride = mk_binop(OP_SUB, up, lw, astb.bnd.dtype);
607 stride = mk_binop(OP_ADD, stride, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
608 ln = mk_binop(OP_MUL, ln, stride, astb.bnd.dtype);
609
610 /* + (j - bnd) --> + j - bnd */
611 ln = mk_binop(OP_ADD, ln, (int)ASD_SUBS(asd, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
612 ln = mk_binop(OP_SUB, ln, lw, astb.bnd.dtype);
613 }
614 if (NO_CHARPTR && DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR) {
615 /* same as if the f77 output is not allowed to have pointers */
616 if (ln != astb.bnd.zero) {
617 print_ast(ln);
618 put_char('+');
619 }
620 if (PTROFFG(asym)) {
621 int offset;
622 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(PTROFFG(asym)));
623 print_ast(offset);
624 } else if (MIDNUMG(asym)) {
625 int offset;
626 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(MIDNUMG(asym)));
627 print_ast(offset);
628 } else {
629 put_int(1);
630 }
631 } else if (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTY(dtype) == TY_DERIVED) {
632 /* same as if the f77 output is not allowed to have pointers */
633 if (ln != astb.bnd.zero) {
634 print_ast(ln);
635 put_char('+');
636 }
637 if (PTROFFG(asym))
638 put_string(SYMNAME(PTROFFG(asym)));
639 else if (MIDNUMG(asym))
640 put_string(SYMNAME(MIDNUMG(asym)));
641 else
642 put_int(1);
643 } else if (!NO_PTR) {
644 /* for f77 output with pointers, need to add '1' to offset
645 * the effect of the target compiler of subtracting 1 from
646 * the linearized subscript expression.
647 */
648 ln = mk_binop(OP_ADD, ln, astb.bnd.one, astb.bnd.dtype);
649 print_ast(ln);
650 } else {
651 /* for f77 output without pointers, add in the 'pointer offset';
652 * added at the end of the subscript expression since the
653 * expression could be 0 or a unary negate. Note that a 1 is
654 * unnecessary since the 'pointer offset' added to the array
655 * is the base address of the allocated array. The subscript
656 * expression is just an offset from the base address.
657 */
658 if (ln != astb.bnd.zero) {
659 print_ast(ln);
660 put_char('+');
661 }
662 if (PTROFFG(asym)) {
663 int offset;
664 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(PTROFFG(asym)));
665 print_ast(offset);
666 } else if (MIDNUMG(asym)) {
667 int offset;
668 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(MIDNUMG(asym)));
669 print_ast(offset);
670 } else {
671 put_int(1);
672 }
673 }
674 put_char(')');
675 op_space = save_op_space;
676 break;
677 } else if (linearize) {
678 /* POINTER or nonPOINTER object has static descriptor */
679 int asym;
680 int dtyp;
681 int lw, off, offset, str, acc1;
682 int nd;
683 LOGICAL no_mult;
684
685 asym = memsym_of_ast(lop);
686 dtyp = DTYPEG(asym);
687 nd = ASD_NDIM(asd);
688 no_mult = FALSE;
689 if (nd == 1 && !POINTERG(asym) &&
690 (!XBIT(58, 0x22) || NEWARGG(asym) == 0) /* not a remapped dummy */
691 && SCG(asym) != SC_DUMMY)
692 no_mult = TRUE;
693 off = 0;
694 if (no_mult) {
695 lw = ASD_SUBS(asd, 0);
696 acc1 = astb.bnd.zero;
697 if (XBIT(58, 0x22) && ADD_LWAST(dtyp, 0))
698 acc1 = mk_binop(OP_SUB, ADD_LWAST(dtyp, 0), astb.bnd.one,
699 astb.bnd.dtype);
700 lw = mk_binop(OP_SUB, lw, acc1, astb.bnd.dtype);
701 if (lw != astb.bnd.zero) {
702 print_ast(lw);
703 off = 1;
704 }
705 } else {
706 for (i = 0; i < nd; i++) {
707 lw = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
708 acc1 = astb.bnd.zero;
709 if (XBIT(58, 0x22) && !POINTERG(asym) && ADD_LWAST(dtyp, i)) {
710 acc1 = mk_binop(OP_SUB, ADD_LWAST(dtyp, i), astb.bnd.one,
711 astb.bnd.dtype);
712 }
713 lw = mk_binop(OP_SUB, lw, acc1, astb.bnd.dtype);
714 str = check_member(lop, get_local_multiplier(linearize, i));
715 if (lw != astb.bnd.zero) {
716 if (off)
717 put_char('+');
718 if (lw != astb.bnd.one) {
719 prec_op = left_precedence(lw, PREC_MULT);
720 if (prec_op < PREC_MULT)
721 put_char('(');
722 print_ast(lw);
723 if (prec_op < PREC_MULT)
724 put_char(')');
725 put_char('*');
726 }
727 print_ast(str);
728 off = 1;
729 }
730 if (F77OUTPUT && XBIT(58, 0x22) && !POINTERG(asym) && NEWARGG(asym)) {
731 /* a remapped dummy array argument;
732 * have to also add section offset */
733 if (off)
734 put_char('+');
735 off = 1;
736 str = check_member(lop, get_section_offset(linearize, i));
737 print_ast(str);
738 }
739 }
740 }
741 if (off)
742 put_char('+');
743 offset = check_member(lop, get_xbase(linearize));
744 print_ast(offset);
745 if (!POINTERG(asym) && SCG(asym) == SC_DUMMY) {
746 put_char(')');
747 op_space = save_op_space;
748 break;
749 }
750
751 if (NO_PTR || (NO_CHARPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_CHAR) ||
752 (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_DERIVED)) {
753 put_char('+');
754 if (PTROFFG(asym)) {
755 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(PTROFFG(asym)));
756 } else {
757 assert(MIDNUMG(asym),
758 "astout:linearize subscripts, midnum & ptroff 0", asym, 3);
759 offset = check_member(lop, mk_id(MIDNUMG(asym)));
760 }
761 print_ast(offset);
762 put_string("-1");
763 }
764
765 put_char(')');
766 op_space = save_op_space;
767 break;
768 }
769 for (i = 0; i < (int)ASD_NDIM(asd) - 1; i++) {
770 print_ast((int)ASD_SUBS(asd, i));
771 put_char(',');
772 }
773 print_ast((int)ASD_SUBS(asd, ASD_NDIM(asd) - 1));
774 put_char(')');
775 op_space = save_op_space;
776 break;
777 case A_SUBSTR:
778 print_ast((int)A_LOPG(ast));
779 put_char('(');
780 if (A_LEFTG(ast))
781 print_ast((int)A_LEFTG(ast));
782 put_char(':');
783 if (A_RIGHTG(ast))
784 print_ast((int)A_RIGHTG(ast));
785 put_char(')');
786 break;
787 case A_TRIPLE:
788 /* [lb]:[ub][:stride] */
789 if (A_LBDG(ast))
790 print_ast((int)A_LBDG(ast));
791 put_char(':');
792 if (A_UPBDG(ast))
793 print_ast((int)A_UPBDG(ast));
794 if (A_STRIDEG(ast)) {
795 put_char(':');
796 print_ast((int)A_STRIDEG(ast));
797 }
798 break;
799 case A_INTR:
800 optype = A_OPTYPEG(ast);
801 if (ast_is_comment) {
802 if (A_ISASSIGNLHSG(ast)) {
803 assert(optype == I_ALLOCATED, "unexpected ISASSIGNLHS", ast, ERR_Fatal);
804 put_call(ast, 0, "allocated_lhs", 0);
805 } else if (A_ISASSIGNLHS2G(ast)) {
806 assert(optype == I_ALLOCATED, "unexpected ISASSIGNLHS2", ast,
807 ERR_Fatal);
808 put_call(ast, 0, "allocated_lhs2", 0);
809 } else {
810 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
811 }
812 break;
813 }
814 if ((sym = EXTSYMG(intast_sym[optype]))) {
815 put_call(ast, 0, SYMNAME(sym), 0);
816 break;
817 }
818 switch (optype) {
819 case I_INT:
820 dtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast));
821 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
822 break;
823 case I_NINT:
824 save_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
825 dtype = DDTG(save_dtype);
826 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
827 break;
828 case I_REAL:
829 save_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
830 dtype = DDTG(save_dtype);
831 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
832 break;
833 case I_AINT:
834 case I_ANINT:
835 save_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
836 dtype = DDTG(save_dtype);
837 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
838 i = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
839 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
840 break;
841 case I_SIZE:
842 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
843 shape = A_SHAPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0));
844 cnt = SHD_NDIM(shape);
845 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_size));
846 put_char('(');
847 put_int((INT)cnt);
848 put_char(',');
849 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 1));
850 for (i = 0; i < cnt - 1; i++) {
851 put_char(',');
852 print_ast((int)SHD_LWB(shape, i));
853 put_char(',');
854 print_ast((int)SHD_UPB(shape, i));
855 put_char(',');
856 print_ast((int)SHD_STRIDE(shape, i));
857 }
858 put_char(',');
859 print_ast((int)SHD_LWB(shape, i));
860 put_char(',');
861 if (SHD_UPB(shape, i))
862 print_ast((int)SHD_UPB(shape, i));
863 else
864 print_ast(astb.ptr0);
865 put_char(',');
866 print_ast((int)SHD_STRIDE(shape, i));
867 put_char(')');
868 break;
869 case I_LBOUND:
870 case I_UBOUND:
871 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
872 shape = A_SHAPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0));
873 cnt = SHD_NDIM(shape);
874 if (optype == I_LBOUND)
875 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lb));
876 else
877 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_ub));
878 put_char('(');
879 put_int((INT)cnt);
880 put_char(',');
881 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 1));
882 for (i = 0; i < cnt; i++) {
883 put_char(',');
884 print_ast((int)SHD_LWB(shape, i));
885 put_char(',');
886 if (SHD_UPB(shape, i))
887 print_ast((int)SHD_UPB(shape, i));
888 else
889 print_ast(astb.ptr0);
890 }
891 put_char(')');
892 break;
893 case I_CMPLX:
894 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
895 if (ARGT_ARG(argt, 2) != 0 && ARGT_ARG(argt, 1) == 0) {
896 /* Kind arg, no second parameter, f90 output */
897 put_string("cmplx");
898 put_char('(');
899 print_ast(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0));
900 put_char(',');
901 put_string("kind");
902 put_char('=');
903 print_ast(ARGT_ARG(argt, 2));
904 put_char(')');
905 break;
906 }
907 save_dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
908 dtype = DDTG(save_dtype);
909 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
910 break;
911 case I_DIMAG:
912 /* since LOP may be aimag, force the name 'dimag' */
913 put_call(ast, 0, "dimag", 0);
914 break;
915 case I_INDEX:
916 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) != 2) {
917 rtlRtn = RTE_indexa;
918 goto make_func_name;
919 }
920 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
921 break;
922 case I_CEILING:
923 case I_MODULO:
924 case I_FLOOR:
925 i = PNMPTRG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))); /* locates "-<name>" */
926 put_call(ast, 0, stb.n_base + i + 1, 0);
927 break;
928 case I_ALLOCATED:
929 rtlRtn = RTE_allocated;
930 goto make_func_name;
931 case I_PRESENT:
932 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 2);
933 break;
934 case I_ACHAR:
935 rtlRtn = RTE_achara;
936 goto make_func_name;
937 case I_EXPONENT:
938 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
939 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)))) == TY_REAL)
940 rtlRtn = RTE_expon;
941#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
942 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)))) == TY_QUAD)
943 rtlRtn = RTE_exponq;
944#endif
945 else
946 rtlRtn = RTE_expond;
947 goto make_func_name;
948 case I_FRACTION:
949 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
950 rtlRtn = RTE_frac;
951#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
952 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
953 rtlRtn = RTE_fracq;
954#endif
955 else
956 rtlRtn = RTE_fracd;
957 goto make_func_name;
958 case I_IACHAR:
959 rtlRtn = RTE_iachara;
960 goto make_func_name;
961 case I_RRSPACING:
962 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
963 rtlRtn = RTE_rrspacing;
964#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
965 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
966 rtlRtn = RTE_rrspacingq;
967#endif
968 else
969 rtlRtn = RTE_rrspacingd;
970 goto make_func_name;
971 case I_SPACING:
972 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
973 rtlRtn = RTE_spacing;
974#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
975 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
976 rtlRtn = RTE_spacingq;
977#endif
978 else
979 rtlRtn = RTE_spacingd;
980 goto make_func_name;
981 case I_NEAREST:
982 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
983 rtlRtn = RTE_nearest;
984#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
985 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
986 rtlRtn = RTE_nearestq;
987#endif
988 else
989 rtlRtn = RTE_nearestd;
990 goto make_func_name;
991 case I_SCALE:
992 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
993 rtlRtn = RTE_scale;
994#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
995 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
996 rtlRtn = RTE_scaleq;
997#endif
998 else
999 rtlRtn = RTE_scaled;
1000 goto make_func_name;
1001 case I_SET_EXPONENT:
1002 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_REAL)
1003 rtlRtn = RTE_setexp;
1004#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
1005 else if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast))) == TY_QUAD)
1006 rtlRtn = RTE_setexpq;
1007#endif
1008 else
1009 rtlRtn = RTE_setexpd;
1010 goto make_func_name;
1011 case I_VERIFY:
1012 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1013 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)))) == TY_CHAR)
1014 rtlRtn = RTE_verifya;
1015 else
1016 rtlRtn = RTE_nverify;
1017 goto make_func_name;
1018 case I_SCAN:
1019 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1020 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)))) == TY_CHAR)
1021 rtlRtn = RTE_scana;
1022 else
1023 rtlRtn = RTE_nscan;
1024 goto make_func_name;
1025 case I_LEN_TRIM:
1026 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1027 if (DTY(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)))) == TY_CHAR)
1028 rtlRtn = RTE_lentrima;
1029 else
1030 rtlRtn = RTE_nlentrim;
1031 goto make_func_name;
1032 case I_ILEN:
1033 rtlRtn = RTE_ilen;
1034 goto make_func_name;
1035#ifdef I_LEADZ
1036 case I_LEADZ:
1037 /* Leadz, popcnt, and poppar are hpf_library and cray
1038 * intrinsics. If the target is a cray, the cray versions supersede
1039 * the hpf versions.
1040 */
1041 if (XBIT(49, 0x1040000)) {
1042 /* T3D/T3E or C90 Cray targets */
1043 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
1044 break;
1045 }
1046 rtlRtn = RTE_leadz;
1047 goto make_func_name;
1048#endif
1049#ifdef I_TRAILZ
1050 case I_TRAILZ:
1051 if (XBIT(49, 0x1040000)) {
1052 /* T3D/T3E or C90 Cray targets */
1053 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
1054 break;
1055 }
1056 rtlRtn = RTE_trailz;
1057 goto make_func_name;
1058#endif
1059#ifdef I_POPCNT
1060 case I_POPCNT:
1061 if (XBIT(49, 0x1040000)) {
1062 /* T3D/T3E or C90 Cray targets */
1063 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
1064 break;
1065 }
1066 rtlRtn = RTE_popcnt;
1067 goto make_func_name;
1068#endif
1069#ifdef I_POPPAR
1070 case I_POPPAR:
1071 if (XBIT(49, 0x1040000)) {
1072 /* T3D/T3E or C90 Cray targets */
1073 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
1074 break;
1075 }
1076 rtlRtn = RTE_poppar;
1077/***** fall thru *****/
1078#endif
1079 make_func_name:
1080 put_call(ast, 0, mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), 0);
1081 break;
1082 case I_RESHAPE:
1083 /* this only occurs if the output is F90 */
1084 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1085 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_reshape));
1086 put_char('(');
1087 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 0));
1088 put_char(',');
1089 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 1));
1090 if (ARGT_ARG(argt, 2)) {
1091 put_char(',');
1092 put_string("pad=");
1093 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 2));
1094 }
1095 if (ARGT_ARG(argt, 3)) {
1096 put_char(',');
1097 put_string("order=");
1098 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, 3));
1099 }
1100 put_char(')');
1101 break;
1102 default:
1103 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 0);
1104 break;
1105 }
1106 break;
1107 case A_ICALL:
1108 if (ast_is_comment) {
1109 put_call(ast, 1, NULL, 0);
1110 break;
1111 }
1112 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
1113 case I_MVBITS:
1114 /* call mvbits(from, frompos, len, to, topos)
1115 * becomes
1116 * call RTE_mvbits(from, frompos, len, to, topos,
1117 * szfrom, szfrompos, szlen, sztopos)
1118 */
1119 put_l_to_u("call ");
1120 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_mvbits));
1121 put_char('(');
1122 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1123 for (i = 0; i <= 4; i++) {
1124 print_ast((int)ARGT_ARG(argt, i));
1125 put_char(',');
1126 }
1127 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* size of from/to */
1128 put_int(size_of(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(lop))));
1129 put_char(',');
1130
1131 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* size of frompos */
1132 put_int(size_of(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(lop))));
1133 put_char(',');
1134
1135 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2); /* size of len */
1136 put_int(size_of(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(lop))));
1137 put_char(',');
1138
1139 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 4); /* size of topos */
1140 put_int(size_of(DDTG(A_DTYPEG(lop))));
1141
1142 put_char(')');
1143 break;
1144
1145 case I_NULLIFY:
1146 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1147 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
1148 sym = find_pointer_variable(lop);
1149 gen_nullify(lop, sym, !NO_PTR && STYPEG(sym) == ST_MEMBER);
1150 break;
1151
1152 case I_PTR2_ASSIGN:
1153 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1154 cnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
1155 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* pointer */
1156 if (A_TYPEG(lop) == A_SUBSCR)
1157 lop = A_LOPG(lop);
1158 sym = find_pointer_variable(lop);
1159 put_l_to_u("call ");
1160 if (DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) != TY_CHAR)
1161 rtlRtn = cnt == 5 ? RTE_ptr_assign : RTE_ptr_assignx;
1162 else
1163 rtlRtn = cnt == 5 ? RTE_ptr_assign_chara : RTE_ptr_assign_charxa;
1164 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn));
1165 put_char('(');
1166
1167 put_mem_string(lop, SYMNAME(sym));
1168 put_char(',');
1169
1170 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
1171 sym = find_pointer_variable(lop);
1172 put_mem_string(lop, SYMNAME(sym)); /* static descriptor */
1173 put_char(',');
1174
1175 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2); /* target */
1176 if (STYPEG(sym) != ST_VAR && A_TYPEG(lop) == A_SUBSCR && A_SHAPEG(lop))
1177 lop = A_LOPG(lop);
1178 print_ast(lop);
1179 put_char(',');
1180
1181 rop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 3); /* target's descriptor */
1182 print_ast(rop);
1183
1184 /* section flag and other datatype arguments */
1185 for (i = 4; i < cnt; ++i) {
1186 put_char(',');
1187 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
1188 print_ast(lop);
1189 }
1190 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
1191 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* descriptor */
1192 sym = find_pointer_variable(lop);
1193 if (DESCARRAYG(sym) && STYPEG(sym) == ST_MEMBER) {
1194 int osym;
1195 osym = VARIANTG(sym);
1196 if (osym > NOSYM && STYPEG(osym) == ST_MEMBER) {
1197 put_char(',');
1198 print_ast_replaced(lop, sym, osym);
1199 osym = VARIANTG(osym);
1200 if (osym > NOSYM && STYPEG(osym) == ST_MEMBER) {
1201 put_char(',');
1202 print_ast_replaced(lop, sym, osym);
1203 }
1204 }
1205 }
1206 }
1207 put_char(')');
1208 break;
1209
1210 case I_PTR_COPYIN:
1211 /* astout needs to generate the call to copy a pointer in since
1212 * printing the ast of the dummy base will result in a subscript
1213 * reference which includes its offset. The argument needs to be
1214 * passed 'as is' (naked base).
1215 */
1216 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1217 sym = A_SPTRG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 3)); /* pointer */
1218 if (DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) != TY_CHAR)
1219 rtlRtn = RTE_ptr_ina;
1220 else
1221 rtlRtn = RTE_ptr_in_chara;
1222 put_l_to_u("call ");
1223 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn));
1224 put_char('(');
1225 /*
1226 * call pghpf_ptr_in(rank, kind, len, db, dd, ab, ad)
1227 *
1228 * example: call pghpf_ptr_in(1,27,4,p,p$sd,p$bs,p$s0)
1229 *
1230 * argt 0: ast of rank (A_CNST)
1231 * argt 1: ast of kind (A_CNST)
1232 * argt 2: ast of len (A_CNST)
1233 * argt 3: ast of dummy base (A_ID) - naked base
1234 * argt 4: ast of dummy static descriptor (A_ID)
1235 * argt 5: ast of actual base (A_ID)
1236 * argt 6: ast of actual static_descriptor (A_ID)
1237 */
1238 i = 0;
1239 while (TRUE) {
1240 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
1241 if (i == 3)
1242 put_string(SYMNAME(sym));
1243 else
1244 print_ast(lop);
1245 i++;
1246 if (i >= 7)
1247 break;
1248 put_char(',');
1249 }
1250 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
1251 if (MIDNUMG(sym)) {
1252 put_char(',');
1253 put_string(SYMNAME(MIDNUMG(sym)));
1254 }
1255 if (PTROFFG(sym)) {
1256 put_char(',');
1257 put_string(SYMNAME(PTROFFG(sym)));
1258 }
1259 }
1260 put_char(')');
1261 break;
1262
1263 case I_PTR_COPYOUT:
1264 /* astout needs to generate the call to copy a pointer out since
1265 * printing the ast of the dummy base will result in a subscript
1266 * reference which includes its offset. The argument needs to be
1267 * passed 'as is' (naked base).
1268 */
1269 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1270 sym = A_SPTRG(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)); /* pointer */
1271 put_l_to_u("call ");
1272 if (DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) != TY_CHAR)
1273 rtlRtn = RTE_ptr_out;
1274 else
1275 rtlRtn = RTE_ptr_out_chara;
1276 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn));
1277 put_char('(');
1278 /*
1279 * call pghpf_ptr_out(ab, ad, db, dd)
1280 *
1281 * example: call pghpf_ptr_out(p$bs, p$s0, p, p$sd)
1282 *
1283 * argt 0: ast of actual base (A_ID) - naked base
1284 * argt 1: ast of actual static descriptor (A_ID)
1285 * argt 2: ast of dummy base (A_ID)
1286 * argt 3: ast of dummy static_descriptor (A_ID)
1287 */
1288 i = 0;
1289 while (TRUE) {
1290 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
1291 if (i == 0)
1292 put_string(SYMNAME(sym));
1293 else
1294 print_ast(lop);
1295 i++;
1296 if (i >= 4)
1297 break;
1298 put_char(',');
1299 }
1300 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
1301 if (MIDNUMG(sym)) {
1302 put_char(',');
1303 put_string(SYMNAME(MIDNUMG(sym)));
1304 }
1305 if (PTROFFG(sym)) {
1306 put_char(',');
1307 put_string(SYMNAME(PTROFFG(sym)));
1308 }
1309 }
1310 put_char(')');
1311 break;
1312 case I_COPYIN:
1313 /* print naked id as 5th argument */
1314 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1315 cnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
1316 put_l_to_u("call ");
1317 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_qopy_in));
1318 put_char('(');
1319 nid = FALSE;
1320 if (XBIT(57, 0x80)) {
1321 int arg2, arg4;
1322 arg2 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2);
1323 arg4 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 4);
1324 if (arg2 == arg4) {
1325 nid = TRUE;
1326 } else if (A_TYPEG(arg2) == A_SUBSCR && A_LOPG(arg2) == arg4) {
1327 nid = TRUE;
1328 }
1329 }
1330 for (i = 0; i < cnt; ++i) {
1331 if (i)
1332 put_char(',');
1333 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
1334 if (nid && (i == 2 || i == 4)) {
1335 print_naked_id(lop);
1336 } else {
1337 print_ast(lop);
1338 }
1339 }
1340 put_char(')');
1341 break;
1342 case I_COPYOUT:
1343 /* print naked id as 1st argument */
1344 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1345 cnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
1346 put_l_to_u("call ");
1347 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_copy_out));
1348 put_char('(');
1349 nid = FALSE;
1350 if (XBIT(57, 0x80)) {
1351 int arg0, arg1;
1352 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
1353 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
1354 if (arg0 == arg1) {
1355 nid = TRUE;
1356 } else if (A_TYPEG(arg1) == A_SUBSCR && A_LOPG(arg1) == arg0) {
1357 nid = TRUE;
1358 }
1359 }
1360 for (i = 0; i < cnt; ++i) {
1361 if (i)
1362 put_char(',');
1363 lop = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
1364 if (nid && (i == 0 || i == 1)) {
1365 print_naked_id(lop);
1366 } else {
1367 print_ast(lop);
1368 }
1369 }
1370 put_char(')');
1371 break;
1372
1373 default:
1374 put_call(ast, 1, NULL, 0);
1375 break;
1376 }
1377 break;
1378 case A_CALL:
1379 put_call(ast, 1, NULL, 1);
1380 break;
1381 case A_FUNC:
1382 put_call(ast, 0, NULL, 1);
1383 break;
1384 case A_ENTRY:
1385 put_l_to_u("entry ");
1386 print_header((int)A_SPTRG(ast));
1387 if (XBIT(49, 0x1000) && !ast_is_comment)
1388 pghpf_entry((int)A_SPTRG(ast));
1389 break;
1390 case A_ASN:
1391 print_ast((int)A_DESTG(ast));
1392 put_string(" = ");

3045
3046static void
3047put_call(int ast, int call, const char *name, int check_ptrarg)
3048{
3049 int dpdsc, paramct, iface;
3050 int sptr, cnt, argt, arg, i, param, sdparam, sdi;
3051 LOGICAL anyoptional, do_naked_pointer, some;
3052 if (call) {
3053 put_l_to_u("call ");
3054 }
3055 if (name) {
3056 put_string(name);
3057 } else {
3058 print_ast(A_LOPG(ast));
3059 }
3060 put_char('(');
3061 sptr = procsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(ast));
3062 proc_arginfo(sptr, &paramct, &dpdsc, &iface);
3063 cnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
3064 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
3065 altret_spec = TRUE;
3066 anyoptional = FALSE;
3067 sdi = -1; /* section descriptor index */
3068 /* f77 output, no pointers allowed, subprogram has a pointer argument */
3069 if (check_ptrarg == 1 && F77OUTPUT && NO_PTR && !ast_is_comment &&
3070 PTRARGG(sptr) && dpdsc > 0 && paramct > 0) {
3071 do_naked_pointer = TRUE;
3072 } else {
3073 do_naked_pointer = FALSE;
3074 }
3075 arg = 0;
3076 some = FALSE;
3077 for (i = 0; i < cnt; ++i) {
3078 /* if there was a previous argument, put comma */
3079 arg = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
3080 if (i >= paramct && dpdsc) {
3081 ++sdi;
3082 {
3083 /* move sdi up to next assumed-shape argument */
3084 while (sdi < paramct) {
3085 sdparam = aux.dpdsc_base[dpdsc + sdi];
3086 if (sdparam && DTY(DTYPEG(sdparam)) == TY_ARRAY &&
3087 ASSUMSHPG(sdparam)) {
3088 break;
3089 } else {
3090 ++sdi;
3091 }
3092 }
3093 }
3094 }
3095 /* separate all arguments with comma */
3096 if (ast_is_comment && i)
3097 put_char(',');
3098 if (arg != 0) {
3099 param = 0;
3100 /* is this a missing optional argument? */
3101 if (i < paramct && dpdsc) {
3102 param = aux.dpdsc_base[dpdsc + i];
3103 }
3104 if (param && OPTARGG(param) && (arg == astb.ptr0 || arg == astb.ptr0c)) {
3105 /* don't print the missing argument */
3106 anyoptional = TRUE;
3107 arg = 0; /* don't print next comma */
3108 } else {
3109 /* separate all arguments with comma, unless already printed above */
3110 if (some && !ast_is_comment)
3111 put_char(',');
3112 some = TRUE;
3113 if (anyoptional) { /* must use keyword form */
3114 if (param) {
3115 put_string(SYMNAME(param));
3116 put_string("=");
3117 } else if (sdi >= 0 && sdi < paramct) {
3118 static char sdname[120];
3119 int sdparam;
3120 sdparam = aux.dpdsc_base[dpdsc + sdi];
3121 strcpy(sdname, SYMNAME(sdparam));
3122 strcat(sdname, "$sd");
3123 put_string(sdname);
3124 put_string("=");
3125 } else {
3126 put_string("NOKEYWORD=");
3127 }
3128 }
3129 if (check_ptrarg == 2 ||
3130 (do_naked_pointer && i < paramct && POINTERG(param))) {
3131 print_naked_id(arg);
3132 } else {
3133 print_ast(arg);
3134 }
3135 }
3136 }
3137 }
3138 altret_spec = FALSE;
3139 put_char(')');
3140} /* put_call */

3142static void
3143print_ast_replaced(int ast, int sym, int replacesym)
3144{
3145 int astreplace;
3146 if (replacesym && STYPEG(replacesym) != ST_MEMBER) {
3147 put_string(SYMNAME(replacesym));
3148 } else {
3149 /* replace 'sym' in 'ast' by 'replacesym', then print it */
3150 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
3151 case A_ID:
3152 case A_CNST:
3153 case A_LABEL:
3154 astreplace = ast;
3155 break;
3156 case A_MEM:
3157 astreplace = A_MEMG(ast);
3158 if (A_TYPEG(astreplace) != A_ID)
3159 astreplace = 0;
3160 break;
3161 case A_SUBSCR:
3162 astreplace = A_LOPG(ast);
3163 if (A_TYPEG(astreplace) == A_MEM) {
3164 astreplace = A_MEMG(astreplace);
3165 }
3166 if (A_TYPEG(astreplace) != A_ID)
3167 astreplace = 0;
3168 break;
3169 default:
3170 astreplace = 0;
3171 break;
3172 }
3173 if (astreplace) {
3174 if (A_SPTRG(astreplace) == sym) {
3175 A_SPTRP(astreplace, replacesym);
3176 } else {
3177 astreplace = 0;
3178 }
3179 }
3180 print_ast(ast);
3181 if (astreplace) {
3182 A_SPTRP(astreplace, sym);
3183 }
3184 }
3185} /* print_ast_replaced */

3241static void
3242print_refsym(int sym, int ast)
3243{
3244 if (F77OUTPUT && !ast_is_comment && !F90POINTERG(sym) &&
3245 (ALLOCG(sym) || SCG(sym) == SC_BASED || /* allocatable symbol */
3246 (STYPEG(sym) == ST_MEMBER && ALIGNG(sym)))) { /*dist member*/
3247 /* pgftn-extensions not allowed: cray pointers not allowed,
3248 * or cray pointers are allowed but the objects can't be character
3249 * or derived type.
3250 */
3251 if (NO_PTR || /* no pointers */
3252 (NO_CHARPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) == TY_CHAR) ||
3253 (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) == TY_DERIVED)) {
3254 put_string(SYMNAME(sym));

3261 int offset;
3262 offset = check_member(ast, mk_id(MIDNUMG(sym)));
3263 print_ast(offset);
3264 }
3265 put_char(')');
3266 return;
3267 }
3268 }
3269 print_sname(sym);
3270 if (DBGBIT(5, 0x40)) {
3271 char b[64];
3272 sprintf(b, "\\%d", sym);
3273 put_string(b);
3274 }

3279{

3282 break;

3285 STYPEG(SCOPEG(SCOPEG(sym))) == ST_MODULE) {
3286 put_string(SYMNAME(SCOPEG(SCOPEG(sym))));
3287 put_string("::");
3288 break;

3290 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
3291 default:
3292 if (ENCLFUNCG(sym) && STYPEG(ENCLFUNCG(sym)) == ST_MODULE) {
3293 put_string(SYMNAME(ENCLFUNCG(sym)));
3294 put_string("::");

3299 case ST_UNKNOWN:
3300 case ST_IDENT:
3301 case ST_VAR:
3302 case ST_ARRAY:
3303 case ST_DESCRIPTOR:
3304 case ST_STRUCT:
3305 case ST_UNION:
3306 if (SCG(sym) == SC_PRIVATE)
3307 put_string("@");
3308 else if (SCG(sym) == SC_BASED && MIDNUMG(sym) &&
3309 SCG(MIDNUMG(sym)) == SC_PRIVATE)
3310 put_string("@");

3328/** \brief Since the output is 'standard' f77, all allocatable (deferred-shape)
3329 arrays must be converted to pointer-based arrays. The symbol table
3330 is scanned to find allocatable arrays which do not have bound temporaries
3331 or associated pointer variables.
3332 */
3333void
3334deferred_to_pointer(void)
3335{
3336 int sptr;
3337 int dtype;
3338 int numdim;
3339 int i;
3340 ADSC *ad;
3341
3342 for (sptr = stb.stg_avail - 1; sptr >= stb.firstusym; sptr--) {
3343 if (STYPEG(sptr) != ST_ARRAY || SCG(sptr) == SC_NONE)
3344 continue;
3345 if (IGNOREG(sptr)) /* ignore this symbol */
3346 continue;
3347 if (F90POINTERG(sptr))
3348 continue;
3349 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3350 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
3351 if (!AD_DEFER(ad) && !AD_NOBOUNDS(ad))
3352 continue;
3353
3354 numdim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
3355 if (!ALIGNG(sptr) && SDSCG(sptr) == 0)
3356 /* if the array has a static descriptor, then never change the
3357 * bounds.
3358 */
3359 for (i = 0; i < numdim; ++i) {
3360 int s;
3361 if (AD_LWAST(ad, i) == 0 || A_TYPEG(AD_LWAST(ad, i)) != A_ID) {
3362 AD_LWAST(ad, i) = mk_bnd_ast();
3363 if (SAVEG(sptr)) {
3364 s = A_SPTRG(AD_LWAST(ad, i));
3365 SCP(s, SC_STATIC);
3366 SAVEP(s, 1);
3367 }
3368 }
3369 if (AD_UPAST(ad, i) == 0 || A_TYPEG(AD_UPAST(ad, i)) != A_ID) {
3370 AD_UPAST(ad, i) = mk_bnd_ast();
3371 if (SAVEG(sptr)) {
3372 s = A_SPTRG(AD_UPAST(ad, i));
3373 SCP(s, SC_STATIC);
3374 SAVEP(s, 1);
3375 }
3376 }
3377 if (AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i) == 0 || A_TYPEG(AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i)) != A_ID) {
3378 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i) = mk_bnd_ast();
3379 if (SAVEG(sptr)) {
3380 s = A_SPTRG(AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i));
3381 SCP(s, SC_STATIC);
3382 SAVEP(s, 1);
3383 }
3384 }
3385 }
3386 /* don't create pointer variable for sequential dummy */
3387 /* or caller remapping dummys */
3388 if (SCG(sptr) == SC_DUMMY) {
3389 if (SEQG(sptr))
3390 continue;
3391 if (XBIT(58, 0x20) && !POINTERG(sptr))
3392 continue;
3393 }
3394 ALLOCP(sptr, 1);
3395 if (MIDNUMG(sptr) == 0) {
3396 int stp;
3397 SCP(sptr, SC_BASED);
3398 stp = sym_get_ptr(sptr);
3399 MIDNUMP(sptr, stp);
3400 }
3401 if (SAVEG(sptr)) {
3402 if (!POINTERG(sptr)) {
3403 SAVEP(MIDNUMG(sptr), 1);
3404 }
3405 if (!NO_PTR)
3406 /* pointers allowed in output! */
3407 SAVEP(sptr, 0); /* based-object cannot be SAVEd */
3408 }
3409 }
3410}

3412static void
3413pr_arr_name(int arr)
3414{
3415 int lop, sptr = 0, dtype;
3416 if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_ID) {
3417 sptr = A_SPTRG(arr);
3418 } else if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_MEM) {
3419 lop = A_PARENTG(arr);
3420 print_ast(lop);
3421 dtype = A_DTYPEG(lop);
3422 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_DERIVED) {
3423 put_char('%');
3424 } else {
3425 put_char('.');
3426 }
3427 sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(arr));
3428 }
3429 print_sname(sptr);
3430} /* pr_arr_name */
3431
3432/* a subscript ast is being processed. First, print the array ('arr') which
3433 * is being subscripted and then check the array to determine if its subscripts
3434 * must be linearized. Returns a non-zero value if the array's subscripts
3435 * must be linearized; 0, otherwise. The non-zero value is 1 for non-POINTER
3436 * arrays; if the array is a POINTER, then the non-zero value is the sym
3437 * pointer representing the POINTER's static descriptor.
3438 */
3439static int
3440pr_chk_arr(int arr)
3441{
3442 int sptr = 0;
3443 if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_ID) {
3444 sptr = A_SPTRG(arr);
3445 } else if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_MEM) {
3446 sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(arr));
3447 } else {
3448 print_ast(arr);
3449 return 0;
3450 }
3451 if (LNRZDG(sptr)) {
3452 /* linearize flag set */
3453 pr_arr_name(arr);
3454 if (SDSCG(sptr) && !NODESCG(sptr))
3455 return SDSCG(sptr);
3456 return 1;
3457 } else if (F77OUTPUT) {
3458 if (ALLOCG(sptr) ||
3459 (SCG(sptr) == SC_BASED &&
3460 (NO_PTR || (NO_CHARPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(sptr)) == TY_CHAR) ||
3461 (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(sptr)) == TY_DERIVED)))) {
3462 pr_arr_name(arr);
3463 if (SDSCG(sptr) && !NODESCG(sptr))
3464 return SDSCG(sptr);
3465 return 1;
3466 }
3467 } else if (ALLOCG(sptr) && SCG(sptr) == SC_BASED &&
3468 (MDALLOCG(sptr) || PTROFFG(sptr))) {
3469 /* linearize subscripts of an allocatable array which came from
3470 * a MODULE.
3471 */
3472 pr_arr_name(arr);
3473 if (SDSCG(sptr) && !NODESCG(sptr))
3474 return SDSCG(sptr);
3475 return 1;
3476 }
3477
3478 pr_arr_name(arr);
3479 return 0;
3480}
3481
3482/* 'sub' is a subscript ast, where the array is allocatable. If the output
3483 * is standard f77, will need to generate assignment statements which assign
3484 * to the array's bound temporaries their respective values. The values are
3485 * presented as 'triple' asts, representing the explicit shape of the array.
3486 * The bound temporaries are extracted from the LWAST and UPAST fields
3487 * of the array's descriptor (ADSC).
3488 */
3489static void
3490gen_bnd_assn(int sub)
3491{
3492 int i, ndim;
3493 int asd;
3494 int asym, dsym;
3495 ADSC *ad;
3496 int triple;
3497 int dtyp;
3498
3499 if (A_TYPEG(sub) != A_SUBSCR) {
3500 return;
3501 }
3502 asd = A_ASDG(sub);
3503 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
3504 asym = memsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(sub));
3505 dsym = DESCRG(asym);
3506 assert(dsym, "gen_bnd_assn: descr not found", asym, 4);
3507 dtyp = DDTG(DTYPEG(asym));
3508 dtyp = get_array_dtype(ndim, dtyp);
3509 DTYPEP(dsym, dtyp);
3510 ad = AD_DPTR(dtyp);
3511 assert(ndim == AD_NUMDIM(ad), "gen_bnd_assn:ndim not equal", asym, 3);
3512 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
3513 triple = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3514 if (A_TYPEG(triple) != A_TRIPLE) {
3515 return;
3516 }
3517 AD_LWAST(ad, i) = A_LBDG(triple);
3518 AD_UPAST(ad, i) = A_UPBDG(triple);
3519 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i) = mk_extent(AD_LWAST(ad, i), AD_UPAST(ad, i), i);
3520 }
3521}
3522
3523static int
3524find_member_base(int dtype)
3525{
3526 int basesptr, dty, mem;
3527 const char *rtnNm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_member_base);
3528 basesptr = lookupsymbol(rtnNm);
3529 if (basesptr == 0 || STYPEG(basesptr) != ST_CMBLK) {
3530 return NOSYM;
3531 }
3532 /* find the member base */
3533 dty = DDTG(dtype);
3534 for (mem = CMEMFG(basesptr); mem > NOSYM; mem = SYMLKG(mem)) {
3535 if (DDTG(DTYPEG(mem)) == dty)
3536 break;
3537 }
3538 return mem;
3539} /* find_member_base */
3540
3541/* If the output is 'standard' f77, need to convert the allocate of an
3542 * object to a call to a run-time routine. 'object' is the ast item
3543 * representing the object; 'stat' is the id ast, not present if 0, of the
3544 * allocate status variable. If 'object' is a subscript ast, the subscripts
3545 * are triples (represents the explicit shape of the allocate); prior to
3546 * calling the run-time routine, the values specified by the explicit
3547 * shape must be assigned to the array's bound temporaries. Otherwise, 'object'
3548 * is an id ast, whose symbol field is the array to be allocate.
3549 * Note that the object is a pointer-based array; the associated pointer
3550 * variable is assigned the pointer of the allocation.
3551 */
3552static void
3553gen_allocate(int object, int stat)
3554{
3555 int i, ndim;
3556 int ast;
3557 int asd;
3558 int asym, dsym, dtype;
3559 ADSC *ad;
3560 int t;
3561 int nelem;
3562 int save_op_space;
3563 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn;
3564 INT ty_val;
3565
3566 if (A_TYPEG(object) == A_SUBSCR) {
3567 asd = A_ASDG(object);
3568 ast = A_LOPG(object);
3569 asym = find_pointer_variable(ast);
3570 dtype = DTYPEG(asym);
3571 dsym = DESCRG(asym);
3572 if (dsym) {
3573 gen_bnd_assn(object);
3574 }
3575 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
3576 nelem = astb.i1;
3577 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++) {
3578 int lw, up, triple, lb, ub, extnt;
3579 triple = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3580 lw = A_LBDG(triple);
3581 if (lw == 0) {
3582 lw = astb.i1;
3583 }
3584 up = A_UPBDG(triple);
3585 if (up == 0) {
3586 up = astb.i1;
3587 }
3588 t = mk_binop(OP_SUB, up, lw, DT_INT);
3589 t = mk_binop(OP_ADD, t, astb.i1, DT_INT);
3590 nelem = mk_binop(OP_MUL, nelem, t, DT_INT);
3591 if (SDSCG(asym) == 0 && !ALIGNG(asym)) {
3592 lb = ADD_LWAST(dtype, i);
3593 if (lb && A_TYPEG(lb) == A_ID && lb != lw) {
3594 /* put out assignment */
3595 put_string(SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(lb)));
3596 put_string(" = ");
3597 print_ast(lw);
3598 }
3599 ub = ADD_UPAST(dtype, i);
3600 if (up && A_TYPEG(ub) == A_ID && ub != up) {
3601 /* put out assignment */
3602 put_string(SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(ub)));
3603 put_string(" = ");
3604 print_ast(up);
3605 }
3606 extnt = ADD_EXTNTAST(dtype, i);
3607 if (extnt && A_TYPEG(extnt) == A_ID) {
3608 /* put out assignment */
3609 put_string(SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(extnt)));
3610 put_string(" = ");
3611 print_ast(mk_extent_expr(lw, up));
3612 }
3613 }
3614 }
3615 } else {
3616 ast = object;
3617 asym = find_pointer_variable(object);
3618 if (STYPEG(asym) == ST_ARRAY) {
3619 ad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(asym));
3620 nelem = AD_NUMELM(ad);
3621 } else
3622 nelem = astb.i1;
3623 }
3624 put_l_to_u("call ");
3625 rtlRtn = !ALLOCG(asym) ? RTE_ptr_alloca : RTE_alloca;
3626 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn));
3627 put_char('(');
3628 save_op_space = op_space;
3629 op_space = FALSE;
3630 print_ast(nelem); /* nelem */
3631 put_char(',');
3632 t = DTYPEG(asym);
3633 t = DTYG(t);
3634 ty_val = ty_to_lib[t];
3635 put_int(ty_val); /* kind */
3636 put_char(',');
3637 print_ast(size_ast(asym, DDTG(DTYPEG(asym)))); /* item length */
3638 put_char(',');
3639 if (stat)
3640 print_ast(stat); /* stat */
3641 else
3642 print_ast(astb.ptr0); /* 'null' stat */
3643 put_char(',');
3644 if (NO_PTR && XBIT(70, 8) && STYPEG(asym) == ST_MEMBER) {
3645 int mem;
3646 if (!F90POINTERG(asym) && POINTERG(asym) && PTROFFG(asym) &&
3647 STYPEG(PTROFFG(asym)) == ST_MEMBER) {
3648 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3649 put_char(',');
3650 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, PTROFFG(asym));
3651 } else {
3652 print_ast(astb.ptr0); /* null pointer */
3653 put_char(',');
3654 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3655 }
3656 put_char(',');
3657 mem = find_member_base(DTYPEG(asym));
3658 if (mem <= NOSYM) {
3659 put_mem_string(ast, SYMNAME(asym));
3660 } else {
3661 put_string(SYMNAME(mem));
3662 }
3663 } else if (NO_PTR || /* no pointers in output */
3664 (NO_CHARPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_CHAR) ||
3665 (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_DERIVED)) {
3666 if (PTROFFG(asym)) {
3667 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3668 put_char(',');
3669 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, PTROFFG(asym));
3670 } else {
3671 print_ast(astb.ptr0); /* null pointer */
3672 put_char(',');
3673 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3674 }
3675 put_char(',');
3676 put_mem_string(ast, SYMNAME(asym));
3677 } else {
3678 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3679 put_char(',');
3680 print_ast(astb.ptr0); /* null offset */
3681 put_char(',');
3682 print_ast(astb.ptr0); /* null base */
3683 }
3684 put_char(')');
3685
3686 if (!F90POINTERG(asym) && POINTERG(asym) && DTY(DTYPEG(asym)) != TY_ARRAY) {
3687 /* assign the run-time type to the static descriptor created for
3688 * the scalar pointer.
3689 */
3690 print_ast_replaced(ast, asym, SDSCG(asym));
3691 put_string("(1) = ");
3692 put_int(ty_val); /* kind */
3693 }
3694
3695 op_space = save_op_space;
3696}
3697
3698/* If the output is 'standard' f77, need to convert the deallocate of an
3699 * object to a call to a run-time routine. 'object' is the id ast
3700 * representing the object; 'stat' is the id ast, not present if 0, of the
3701 * allocate status variable.
3702 * Note that the object is a pointer-based array; the associated pointer
3703 * variable is passed to the run-time routine.
3704 */
3705static void
3706gen_deallocate(int object, int stat, int asym, int passptr)
3707{
3708 assert(A_TYPEG(object) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(object) == A_MEM,
3709 "gen_deallocate:exp.id ast", object, 3);
3710 put_l_to_u("call ");
3711 if (passptr && MIDNUMG(asym) == 0) {
3712 passptr = 0;
3713 }
3714 if (passptr) {
3715 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_deallocx));
3716 } else {
3717 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_dealloca));
3718 }
3719 put_char('(');
3720 if (stat)
3721 print_ast(stat);
3722 else
3723 print_ast(astb.ptr0);
3724 put_char(',');
3725 if (NO_PTR && XBIT(70, 8) && STYPEG(asym) == ST_MEMBER) {
3726 int mem;
3727 mem = find_member_base(DTYPEG(asym));
3728 if (mem <= NOSYM) {
3729 put_mem_string(object, SYMNAME(asym));
3730 } else {
3731 put_string(SYMNAME(mem));
3732 }
3733 put_char('(');
3734 if (!F90POINTERG(asym) && POINTERG(asym) && PTROFFG(asym) &&
3735 STYPEG(PTROFFG(asym)) == ST_MEMBER) {
3736 print_ast_replaced(object, asym, PTROFFG(asym));
3737 } else {
3738 print_ast_replaced(object, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3739 }
3740 put_char(')');
3741 } else if (NO_PTR || /* no pointers in output */
3742 (NO_CHARPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_CHAR) ||
3743 (NO_DERIVEDPTR && DTYG(DTYPEG(asym)) == TY_DERIVED)) {
3744 put_mem_string(object, SYMNAME(asym));
3745 put_char('(');
3746 if (PTROFFG(asym))
3747 print_ast_replaced(object, asym, PTROFFG(asym));
3748 else
3749 print_ast_replaced(object, asym, MIDNUMG(asym));
3750 put_char(')');
3751 } else if (passptr) {
3752 put_mem_string(object, SYMNAME(MIDNUMG(asym)));
3753 } else {
3754 put_mem_string(object, SYMNAME(asym));
3755 }
3756 put_char(')');
3757 if (POINTERG(asym) || passptr) {
3758 if (!NO_PTR || !XBIT(70, 8) || STYPEG(asym) != ST_MEMBER)
3759 gen_nullify(object, asym, passptr);
3760 }
3761}
3762
3763static void
3764gen_nullify(int ast, int sym, int passptr)
3765{
3766 /* Pointer disassociation (statement):
3767 * nullify(pv)
3768 * call pghpf_nullify(pv, pv$sdsc)
3769 * pv: base.
3770 * pv$sdsc: pv's (new) static descriptor
3771 */
3772 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn;
3773
3774 if (F90POINTERG(sym)) {
3775 put_l_to_u("nullify( ");
3776 put_mem_string(ast, SYMNAME(sym));
3777 put_char(')');
3778 return;
3779 }
3780 if (STYPEG(sym) == ST_MEMBER) {
3781 /* do the nullify in-line */
3782 if (MIDNUMG(sym)) {
3783 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, MIDNUMG(sym));
3784 put_string(" = 0");
3785 }
3786 if (PTROFFG(sym)) {
3787 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, PTROFFG(sym));
3788 put_string(" = 0");
3789 }
3790 if (SDSCG(sym)) {
3791 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, SDSCG(sym));
3792 put_string("(1) = 0");
3793 }
3794 return;
3795 }
3796 put_l_to_u("call ");
3797 if (DTYG(DTYPEG(sym)) == TY_CHAR) {
3798 rtlRtn = RTE_nullify_chara;
3799 } else if (passptr) {
3800 rtlRtn = RTE_nullifyx;
3801 } else {
3802 rtlRtn = RTE_nullify;
3803 }
3804 put_string(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn));
3805 put_char('(');
3806
3807 if (passptr) {
3808 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, MIDNUMG(sym));
3809 } else {
3810 put_mem_string(ast, SYMNAME(sym));
3811 }
3812 put_char(',');
3813
3814 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, SDSCG(sym));
3815 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
3816 if (MIDNUMG(sym)) {
3817 put_char(',');
3818 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, MIDNUMG(sym));
3819 }
3820 if (PTROFFG(sym)) {
3821 put_char(',');
3822 print_ast_replaced(ast, sym, PTROFFG(sym));
3823 }
3824 }
3825 put_char(')');
3826}

3872
3873static void
3874put_const(int sptr)
3875{
3876 int len; /* length of character string */
3877 char b[64];
3878 char *from;
3879 int c;
3880 int dtype;
3881 int sptr2;
3882
3883 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3884 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
3885 case TY_WORD:
3886 sprintf(b, "z'%x'", CONVAL2G(sptr));
3887 put_l_to_u(b);
3888 return;
3889 case TY_DWORD:
3890 sprintf(b, "z'%x%08x'", CONVAL1G(sptr), CONVAL2G(sptr));
3891 put_l_to_u(b);
3892 return;
3893 case TY_BINT:
3894 case TY_SINT:
3895 case TY_INT:
3896 put_intkind(CONVAL2G(sptr), dtype);
3897 return;
3898 case TY_BLOG:
3899 case TY_SLOG:
3900 case TY_LOG:
3901 case TY_LOG8:
3902 put_logical(CONVAL2G(sptr), dtype);
3903 return;
3904 case TY_INT8:
3905 put_int8(sptr);
3906 return;
3907 case TY_REAL:
3908 if (NMPTRG(sptr)) {
3909 put_string(SYMNAME(sptr));
3910 return;
3911 }
3912 put_float(CONVAL2G(sptr));
3913 return;
3914
3915 case TY_DBLE:
3916 if (NMPTRG(sptr)) {
3917 put_string(SYMNAME(sptr));
3918 return;
3919 }
3920 put_double(sptr);
3921 return;
3922
3923 case TY_CMPLX:
3924 if (NMPTRG(sptr)) {
3925 put_string(SYMNAME(sptr));
3926 return;
3927 }
3928 put_char('(');
3929 put_float(CONVAL1G(sptr));
3930 put_char(',');
3931 put_float(CONVAL2G(sptr));
3932 put_char(')');
3933 return;
3934
3935 case TY_DCMPLX:
3936 if (NMPTRG(sptr)) {
3937 put_string(SYMNAME(sptr));
3938 return;
3939 }
3940 put_char('(');
3941 put_const((int)CONVAL1G(sptr));
3942 put_char(',');
3943 put_const((int)CONVAL2G(sptr));
3944 put_char(')');
3945 return;
3946
3947 case TY_HOLL:
3948 sptr2 = CONVAL1G(sptr);
3949 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr2);
3950 from = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr2);
3951 len = string_length(dtype);
3952 sprintf(b, "%d", len);
3953 put_string(b);
3954 b[0] = CONVAL2G(sptr); /* kind of hollerith - 'h', 'l', or 'r' */
3955 b[1] = '\0';
3956 put_l_to_u(b);
3957 while (len--) {
3958 c = *from++ & 0xff;
3959 put_char(c);
3960 }
3961 return;
3962
3963 case TY_NCHAR:
3964 sptr = CONVAL1G(sptr); /* sptr to char string constant */
3965 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3966 put_l_to_u("nc");
3967 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
3968 case TY_CHAR:
3969 from = stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr);
3970 put_char('\'');
3971 len = string_length(dtype);
3972 while (len--)
3973 char_to_text(*from++);
3974 put_char('\'');
3975 return;
3976
3977 case TY_PTR:
3978 strcpy(b, "address constant");
3979 break;
3980
3981 default:
3982 strcpy(b, "bad_const_type");
3983 }
3984
3985 put_string(b);
3986}

4108
4109static void
4110put_float(INT val)
4111{
4112 char b[64];
4113 char *start;
4114 char *end;
4115 int i;
4116 char *exp;
4117 int expw;
4118
4119 /* FIXME double cast is done to silence the warning, this needs to be
4120 * revisited! cprintf (our cprintf, not system routine) takes a pointer but
4121 * in this particular case uses is as an integer
4122 */
4123 cprintf(b, "%.10e", (INT *)((BIGINT)val));
4124 for (start = b; *start == ' '; start++) /* skip leading blanks */
4125 ;
4126 /* only leave the sign if it's '-' */
4127 if (*start == '+')
4128 start++;
4129
4130 /* locate beginning of exponent */
4131 exp = &b[strlen(b) - 1];
4132 expw = -1; /* width of exponent less 'E' and the sign */
4133 while (*exp != 'E' && *exp != 'e' && *exp != 'D' && *exp != 'd') {
4134 if (exp <= start) {
4135 /* output from cprintf is [-]INF */
4136 if (*start == '-')
4137 put_char('-');
4138 put_string("1e+39");
4139 return;
4140 }
4141 exp--;
4142 expw++;
4143 }
4144
4145 i = (exp - b) - 1; /* last decimal digit */
4146 /*
4147 * omit trailing 0's; don't omit digit after the decimal point.
4148 */
4149 while (b[i] == '0' && i > 3)
4150 i--;
4151 end = &b[i + 1];
4152 /* exp locates 'E' */
4153 *end++ = 'e';
4154 if (*++exp == '-') /* sign */
4155 *end++ = '-';
4156 if (expw == 2) {
4157 if (*++exp != '0')
4158 *end++ = *exp;
4159 *end++ = *++exp;
4160 } else {
4161 while (expw--)
4162 *end++ = *++exp;
4163 }
4164 if (DTY(DT_REAL) != TY_REAL) {
4165 /* f90 output */
4166 *end++ = '_';
4167 sprintf(end, "%d", target_kind(DT_REAL4));
4168 } else
4169 *end = '\0';
4170 put_string(start);
4171}
4172
4173static void
4174put_double(int sptr)
4175{
4176 INT num[2];
4177 char b[64];
4178 char *start;
4179 char *end;
4180 char *exp;
4181 int expw;
4182 int i;
4183
4184 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
4185 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4186
4187 /* warning: there may be 2 or digits in the exponent -- D<sign>dd or
4188 * D<sign>ddd.
4189 */
4190
4191 if (XBIT(49, 0x40000)) /* C90 */
4192 cprintf(b, "%.15ld", num);
4193 else
4194 cprintf(b, "%.17ld", num);
4195
4196 for (start = b; *start == ' '; start++) /* skip leading blanks */
4197 ;
4198 /* only leave the sign if it's '-' */
4199 if (*start == '+')
4200 start++;
4201
4202 /* locate beginning of exponent */
4203 exp = &b[strlen(b) - 1];
4204 expw = -1; /* width of exponent less 'D' and the sign */
4205 while (*exp != 'E' && *exp != 'e' && *exp != 'D' && *exp != 'd') {
4206 if (exp <= start) {
4207 /* output from cprintf is [-]INF */
4208 if (*start == '-')
4209 put_char('-');
4210 put_string("1d+309");
4211 return;
4212 }
4213 exp--;
4214 expw++;
4215 }
4216
4217 i = (exp - b) - 1; /* last decimal digit */
4218 /*
4219 * omit trailing 0's; don't omit digit after the decimal point.
4220 */
4221 while (b[i] == '0' && i > 3)
4222 i--;
4223 end = &b[i + 1];
4224 /* exp locates 'D' */
4225 if (DTY(DT_REAL) == TY_DBLE && XBIT(49, 0x800000))
4226 /* change 'd' to 'e' only if default real is double precision for
4227 * the cray systems.
4228 */
4229 *end++ = 'e';
4230 else
4231 *end++ = 'd';
4232 if (*++exp == '-') /* sign */
4233 *end++ = '-';
4234 if (expw == 2) {
4235 if (*++exp != '0')
4236 *end++ = *exp;
4237 *end++ = *++exp;
4238 } else {
4239 while (expw--)
4240 *end++ = *++exp;
4241 }
4242 *end = '\0';
4243 put_string(start);
4244}

4246/*
4247 * emit a character with consideration given to the ', escape sequences,
4248 * unprintable characters, etc.
4249 */
4250static void
4251char_to_text(int ch)
4252{
4253 int c;
4254 char b[8];
4255
4256 c = ch & 0xff;
4257 if (c == '\\' && !XBIT(124, 0x40)) {
4258 put_char('\\');
4259 put_char('\\');
4260 } else if (c == '\'') {
4261 put_char('\'');
4262 put_char('\'');
4263 } else if (c >= ' ' && c <= '~')
4264 put_char(c);
4265 else if (XBIT(52, 0x10)) {
4266 put_char(c);
4267 } else if (c == '\n') {
4268 put_char('\\');
4269 put_char('n');
4270 } else if (c == '\t') {
4271 put_char('\\');
4272 put_char('t');
4273 } else if (c == '\v') {
4274 put_char('\\');
4275 put_char('v');
4276 } else if (c == '\b') {
4277 put_char('\\');
4278 put_char('b');
4279 } else if (c == '\r') {
4280 put_char('\\');
4281 put_char('r');
4282 } else if (c == '\f') {
4283 put_char('\\');
4284 put_char('f');
4285 } else {
4286 /* Mask off 8 bits worth of unprintable character */
4287 sprintf(b, "\\%03o", c);
4288 put_string(b);
4289 }
4290}

4343static char *
4344label_name(int lab)
4345{
4346 char *nm;
4347 char lbuff[8];
4348 static int lbavail = 99999;
4349
4350 nm = SYMNAME(lab);
4351 if (CCSYMG(lab)) {
4352 /* compiler-created label - ensure that its number doesn't conflict
4353 * with a user label.
4354 */
4355 int lb;
4356
4357 if (SYMLKG(lab))
4358 /* one is already created */
4359 lb = SYMLKG(lab);
4360 else {
4361 lbuff[0] = '.'; /* user label begins with '.L' */
4362 strcpy(&lbuff[1], nm + 1); /* copy 'L' followed by the digits */
4363 /*
4364 * search for a label which doesn't conflict.
4365 */
4366 while (TRUE) {
4367 if (lookupsym(lbuff, 7) == 0)
4368 break;
4369 sprintf(&lbuff[2], "%05d", lbavail--);
4370 }
4371 lb = getsym(lbuff, 7);
4372 STYPEP(lb, ST_LABEL);
4373 SYMLKP(lab, lb);
4374 }
4375 nm = SYMNAME(lb);
4376 }
4377 nm += 2; /* skip past .L */
4378 while (*nm == '0')
4379 nm++; /* skip over leading 0's */
4380 return nm;
4381}
